message: Let's split it 50/50, a fair start!
You're starting strong, I'll try to counter!
You're trying to take the lead, but I'll try to balance it out!
You're trying to balance it out, but I'm still aiming high!
You're trying to take the lead, but I'll try to stay close!
You're trying to stay close, but I'm pushing for the lead!
You're pushing for the lead, but I'll try to catch up!
You're trying to catch up, but I'm not letting up!
You're not letting up, but I'll try to stay in the game!
You're trying to stay in the game, but I'm making my final push!
You're making your final push, but I'll try to make a last stand!
Last chance, take it or leave it!
